{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/css-header/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Zero Forest"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f28d9b60-8cdc-5c2c-9110-80387ef7b0bd","excerpt":"CSSのコピペだけで反映できる、簡単な見出しデザインを用意しました。\nフォントのサイズや色はご自由に変更ください。 見出しデザインを設定するには この記事で紹介するデザインを使う時には、HTMLに見出しタグ(h…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E8%A6%8B%E5%87%BA%E3%81%97%E3%83%87%E3%82%B6%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3%E3%82%92%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E3%81%AB%E3%81%AF\">見出しデザインを設定するには</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/css-header/#%E3%82%B7%E3%83%B3%E3%83%97%E3%83%AB%E3%81%AA%E3%83%87%E3%82%B6%E3%82%A4%E3%83%B3\">シンプルなデザイン</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E3%81%AB%E7%B7%9A%E3%82%92%E5%BC%95%E3%81%8F\">上下に線を引く</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E4%BA%8C%E9%87%8D%E3%81%AE%E7%B7%9A%E3%82%92%E5%BC%95%E3%81%8F\">二重の線を引く</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E5%B7%A6%E5%8F%B3%E3%81%AB%E7%B7%9A%E3%82%92%E5%BC%95%E3%81%8F\">左右に線を引く</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E7%B7%9A%E3%81%AE%E5%A4%AA%E3%81%95%E3%82%92%E5%A4%89%E3%81%88%E3%82%8B\">線の太さを変える</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF%E3%81%AE%E8%89%B2%E3%82%92%E5%A4%89%E3%81%88%E3%82%8B\">背景の色を変える</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E3%81%A1%E3%82%87%E3%81%A3%E3%81%A8%E3%81%9A%E3%82%89%E3%81%97%E3%81%A6%E3%81%BF%E3%82%8B\">ちょっとずらしてみる</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%97\">ストライプ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/css-header/#%E3%82%B9%E3%83%88%E3%83%A9%E3%82%A4%E3%83%97%E3%81%AE%E4%B8%8B%E7%B7%9A%E3%82%92%E3%81%B2%E3%81%8F\">ストライプの下線をひく</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","html":"<p>CSSのコピペだけで反映できる、簡単な見出しデザインを用意しました。\nフォントのサイズや色はご自由に変更ください。</p>\n<h2 id=\"見出しデザインを設定するには\" style=\"position:relative;\">見出しデザインを設定するには</h2>\n<p>この記事で紹介するデザインを使う時には、HTMLに見出しタグ(h2)を入れてください。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>見出しのデザイン<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>見出しタグは記事以外にも使われている場合があります。 もし余計な場所も装飾されてしまうようでしたら、\nCSSのh2{の前に、article h2{や.post h2{と記事用のクラスをつけてください。</p>\n<h2 id=\"シンプルなデザイン\" style=\"position:relative;\">シンプルなデザイン</h2>\n<h3 id=\"上下に線を引く\" style=\"position:relative;\">上下に線を引く</h3>\n<p>シンプルですが、とても使いやすいデザインです。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 18.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"上下線の見出しサンプル\"\n        title=\"上下線の見出しサンプル\"\n        src=\"/static/a47b154dcab25305f21df0646a6f46e4/c08c5/20180822-header-05b.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a47b154dcab25305f21df0646a6f46e4/e07e9/20180822-header-05b.jpg 200w,\n/static/a47b154dcab25305f21df0646a6f46e4/066f9/20180822-header-05b.jpg 400w,\n/static/a47b154dcab25305f21df0646a6f46e4/c08c5/20180822-header-05b.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>文字と線の色を揃えるのもかわいいですよ。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2{\n    margin:30px;\n    padding:12px;\n    color:#F08972;\n    text-align:center;\n    border-top:1px solid #F08972;\n    border-bottom:1px solid #F08972;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"二重の線を引く\" style=\"position:relative;\">二重の線を引く</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.499999999999996%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"二重線の見出しサンプル\"\n        title=\"二重線の見出しサンプル\"\n        src=\"/static/579748d4b53cb03afdabff5260a1e13e/c08c5/20180822-header-02.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/579748d4b53cb03afdabff5260a1e13e/e07e9/20180822-header-02.jpg 200w,\n/static/579748d4b53cb03afdabff5260a1e13e/066f9/20180822-header-02.jpg 400w,\n/static/579748d4b53cb03afdabff5260a1e13e/c08c5/20180822-header-02.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2{\n    margin:30px;\n    padding:12px;\n    text-align:center;\n    border-top:4px double #DDD;\n    border-bottom:4px double #DDD;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"左右に線を引く\" style=\"position:relative;\">左右に線を引く</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"左右線の見出しサンプル\"\n        title=\"左右線の見出しサンプル\"\n        src=\"/static/214e003935cd2abbb5307669406d01a7/c08c5/20180822-header-03.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/214e003935cd2abbb5307669406d01a7/e07e9/20180822-header-03.jpg 200w,\n/static/214e003935cd2abbb5307669406d01a7/066f9/20180822-header-03.jpg 400w,\n/static/214e003935cd2abbb5307669406d01a7/c08c5/20180822-header-03.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2{\n    text-align:center;\n}\nh2:before,\nh2:after {\n    content:\"\";\n    display:inline-block;\n    width:120px; height:1px;\n    margin:0 10px;\n    background-color: #DDD;\n    vertical-align: middle;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>marginを大きくすると、タイトルと線の間がもっと広げることもできます。\nwidthで線の長さを調整できます。</p>\n<h3 id=\"線の太さを変える\" style=\"position:relative;\">線の太さを変える</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 12.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"二重線の見出しサンプル２\"\n        title=\"二重線の見出しサンプル２\"\n        src=\"/static/b562534dedf05dd28caaa0e58903fcfe/c08c5/20180822-header-04b.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b562534dedf05dd28caaa0e58903fcfe/e07e9/20180822-header-04b.jpg 200w,\n/static/b562534dedf05dd28caaa0e58903fcfe/066f9/20180822-header-04b.jpg 400w,\n/static/b562534dedf05dd28caaa0e58903fcfe/c08c5/20180822-header-04b.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2 {\n    position: relative;\n    padding: 12px;\n    text-align:center;\n}\nh2:before,\nh2:after {\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 0;\n    content: '';\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 6px;\n    box-sizing:\n    border-box;\n}\nh2:before {\n    top: 0;\n    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;\n    border-bottom: 2px solid #ddd;\n}\nh2:after {\n    bottom: 0;\n    border-top: 2px solid #ddd;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"背景の色を変える\" style=\"position:relative;\">背景の色を変える</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 13%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"見出しサンプル\"\n        title=\"見出しサンプル\"\n        src=\"/static/e363ea284205081cd0dbdb072c286384/c08c5/20180822-header-05.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e363ea284205081cd0dbdb072c286384/e07e9/20180822-header-05.jpg 200w,\n/static/e363ea284205081cd0dbdb072c286384/066f9/20180822-header-05.jpg 400w,\n/static/e363ea284205081cd0dbdb072c286384/c08c5/20180822-header-05.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2 {\n    position: relative;\n    text-align:center;\n    color:#FFF;\n    padding: 10px;\n    background-color: #8BC0B8;\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 0px 6px #8BC0B8;\n    border-top: 1px solid #fff;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #fff;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ちょっとずらしてみる\" style=\"position:relative;\">ちょっとずらしてみる</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 25.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"見出しサンプル（色をずれた）\"\n        title=\"見出しサンプル（色をずれた）\"\n        src=\"/static/ce2dcd807df1ce971e95a96bcf1875a3/c08c5/20180822-header-06.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/ce2dcd807df1ce971e95a96bcf1875a3/e07e9/20180822-header-06.jpg 200w,\n/static/ce2dcd807df1ce971e95a96bcf1875a3/066f9/20180822-header-06.jpg 400w,\n/static/ce2dcd807df1ce971e95a96bcf1875a3/c08c5/20180822-header-06.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2 {\n    position:relative;\n    margin:10px;\n    display:inline-block;\n    padding:10px 60px;\n    border:1px solid #DDD;\n    background:none;\n}\nh2:after {\n    position: absolute;\n    top:2px;\n    left:6px;\n    content:\"\";\n    height:100%;\n    width:100%;\n    z-index:-999;\n    -webkit-transform: rotate(-1deg);\n    -moz-transform: rotate(-1deg);\n    background:#FBDDC8;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ストライプ\" style=\"position:relative;\">ストライプ</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 13.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ストライプの見出しサンプル\"\n        title=\"ストライプの見出しサンプル\"\n        src=\"/static/f61205fee3f1dc27a2495efafadaab01/c08c5/20180822-header-07.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f61205fee3f1dc27a2495efafadaab01/e07e9/20180822-header-07.jpg 200w,\n/static/f61205fee3f1dc27a2495efafadaab01/066f9/20180822-header-07.jpg 400w,\n/static/f61205fee3f1dc27a2495efafadaab01/c08c5/20180822-header-07.jpg 640w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markup\"><pre class=\"language-markup\"><code class=\"language-markup\">h2{\n    position: relative;\n    text-align:center;\n    padding: 10px;\n    color:#474342;\n    background: -webkit-repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, #EFC4C0, #EFC4C0 6px,#F6DED4 6px, #F6DED4 12px);\n    background: repeating-linear-gradient(-45deg, #FBDDC8, #FBDDC8 6px,#F6BCAC 6px, #F6BCAC 12px);\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"ストライプの下線をひく\" style=\"position:relative;\">ストライプの下線をひく</h3>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 640px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 16.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"ストライプ下線の見出しサンプル\"\n     